Employee Recognition Application - Power Platform Project
Copyright 2025 Kyle J. Coder

This product includes software developed by Kyle J. Coder
for the VA healthcare system.

Original work created as part of the VHA Informatics Data Team
employee recognition solution development project.

This software contains the following components:

1. Power Apps Canvas Application
   - Employee Recognition submission and management interface
   - Award-specific workflow logic and user experience design
   - Mobile-responsive design and accessibility features

2. Power Automate Flows
   - Safety Check Chatbot with AI-powered guidance
   - Triage and Approval Routing automation
   - Teams and Outlook integration workflows

3. SharePoint Integration Components
   - List configurations and data structure design
   - Permission frameworks and security models
   - Audit logging and compliance tracking systems

4. Documentation and Training Materials
   - Comprehensive technical documentation
   - User training presentations and guides
   - Professional repository organization and best practices

5. Enterprise Architecture Design
   - Multi-environment deployment strategy
   - Security compliance framework
   - Application lifecycle management procedures

All original code, documentation, architecture design, and implementation
patterns are the intellectual property of Kyle J. Coder and are licensed
under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

